name: Ottez United Banner
description:
This is a gift to all who participated in the Ottez United event.
The tickets sold were strictly for the composition and experience given to Ottez holders.
Each Ottez owner gave permission for use in this image and received this NFT to memorialize the occasion. These are memes and were not original art listed for sale on primary.

Thank you all for making the Ottez Community such a fun place to be.
